description:
#ArtWithAim What’s it going to take for people to finally realize that they’ve been bamboozled, by psychopaths in power, on a grand scale?! How on earth are the radically righteous, wildly misinformed, Covid mask mandating zombies among us going to come to terms with this, and admit how wrong they’ve been? Accepting that morbidly wealthy, monopolizing transnational, predatory corporations and their political puppets are power grabbing vampires was something I did long ago... but watching the covid cult overtake nearly everyone around me, and around the western world... without even the basic research, basic questions, or pushback has pushed me to the edge of my sanity.
